data.description: Remodeled! Recently added recessed lights in the living room, dining room and kitchen. Come home to this quiet, private, light-filled condo with a balcony.  From the tile-refinished floors, new carpeted bedrooms, master bedroom has walk in closet, renovated bathrooms, and stainless-steel appliances, this home is full of beautiful updates. The kitchen has New Dishwasher, New Range Hood, and Double Sink with the garbage disposal. The living and dining room has laminate floors and a wood-burning fireplace with glass doors.  HVAC system is only 5 years old.  This place offers two parking spaces, a stackable washer and dryer and a Ring security alarm system.    This well-managed condo complex has playgrounds, a pool and clubhouse, and open green space. The association does a great job maintaining the landscaping and the exterior of the buildings. From here, you have easy access to the W&OD trail just outside your door and two breweries and restaurants that are within 2 miles. Come on home! There is a storage room on the first level size: 4' x 6' that belongs to the property.
